      Conserved Core Circuit Motifs & Architectures
        ::icon(fa fa-project-diagram)
        Evidence: Highly conserved circuits (e.g., habenula-interpeduncular) across vertebrates
        Basic cell types and areal organization show conservation
      Species-Specific Divergence in Fine Details
        ::icon(fa fa-code-branch)
